            "caption": "The text content from the image is as follows:\n\n\"Table 4. F-measure values obtained over different IoU thresholds, from 0.5 to 0.95, in the counter detection stage. Note that Fast-YOLOv4-SmallObj achieves considerably better results at higher IoU thresholds (i.e., 0.8-0.95), which indicates that its predictions are much better aligned with the ground truth.\"",
            "footnote": "",
            "latex": "",
            "html": "<html>\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Model</td>\n    <td>0.5</td>\n    <td>0.6</td>\n    <td>0.7</td>\n    <td>0.8</td>\n    <td>0.9</td>\n    <td>0.95</td>\n    <td>0.5：0.95</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>UF PR-AMR[3]</td>\n    <td>Fast-YOLO v4(608x608)</td>\n    <td>98.1%</td>\n    <td>97.8%</td>\n    <td>97.6%</td>\n    <td>94.6%</td>\n    <td>75.9%</td>\n    <td>38.6%</td>\n    <td>83.8%</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Fast-YOLO v4-Small Obj</td>\n    <td>99.9%</td>\n    <td>99.9%</td>\n    <td>99.9%</td>\n    <td>98.1%</td>\n    <td>80.0%</td>\n    <td>38.9%</td>\n    <td>86.1%</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Copel-AMR</td>\n    <td>Fast-YOLO v4(608x608)</td>\n    <td>99.0%</td>\n    <td>98.3%</td>\n    <td>95.3%</td>\n    <td>84.2%</td>\n    <td>52.2%</td>\n    <td>17.0%</td>\n    <td>74.3%</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Fast-YOLO v4-Small Obj</td>\n    <td>99.7%</td>\n    <td>99.5%</td>\n    <td>98.8%</td>\n    <td>96.1%</td>\n    <td>75.3%</td>\n    <td>28.8%</td>\n    <td>83.0%</td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n</html>",
