            "caption": "The text content from the image is as follows:\n\n\"Table 6. Results achieved by CDCC-NET in the counter classification task. It is able to filter out 98.9% of the illegible/faulty meters, while correctly accepting 99.82% (on average of both datasets) of the legible/operational meters.\"",
